{"ja371:0.1":"Jataka ","ja371:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","ja371:0.3":"Addhavagga ","ja371:0.4":"1. Dighitikosalajataka ","ja371:1.1":"“Evambhutassa te raja, ","ja371:1.2":"agatassa vase mama; ","ja371:1.3":"Atthi nu koci pariyayo, ","ja371:1.4":"yo tam dukkha pamocaye”. ","ja371:2.1":"“Evambhutassa me tata, ","ja371:2.2":"agatassa vase tava; ","ja371:2.3":"Natthi no koci pariyayo, ","ja371:2.4":"yo mam dukkha pamocaye”. ","ja371:3.1":"“Nannam sucaritam raja, ","ja371:3.2":"nannam raja subhasitam; ","ja371:3.3":"Tayate maranakale, ","ja371:3.4":"evamevitaram dhanam. ","ja371:4.1":"Akkocchi mam avadhi mam, ","ja371:4.2":"ajini mam ahasi me; ","ja371:4.3":"Ye ca tam upanayhanti, ","ja371:4.4":"veram tesam na sammati. ","ja371:5.1":"Akkocchi mam avadhi mam, ","ja371:5.2":"ajini mam ahasi me; ","ja371:5.3":"Ye ca tam nupanayhanti, ","ja371:5.4":"veram tesupasammati. ","ja371:6.1":"Na hi verena verani, ","ja371:6.2":"sammantidha kudacanam; ","ja371:6.3":"Averena ca sammanti, ","ja371:6.4":"esa dhammo sanantano”ti. ","ja371:7.1":"Dighitikosalajatakam pathamam. "}